A VIDEO of a traffic cop in full uniform assaulting an allegedly drunk man has emerged on social media. The cop, attached to the Makhuduthamaga Municipality in Limpopo, can be seen in the video giving two warm klaps to the helpless man before trapping him to the ground. The motive behind the incident is still unclear. The incident allegedly happened over the weekend at a filling station in Jane Furse Matome Moremi-Taueatsoala, a spokesman for the transport department in Limpopo, said the cop works for Makhuduthamaga municipal traffic and not the provincial traffic department. Moremi-Taueatsoala added that the municipality will soon release a statement on the matter. 